Linter - SKUEL


  Problem Identified: The SKUEL pattern linter was reporting 12 violations in itself - all legitimate meta-references needed to detect patterns (comments, docstrings, regex patterns, error messages).

  Root Cause: Exclusion logic bug in _find_python_files() method (line 105):
  # BEFORE (Bug)
  if any(excluded in py_file.parts for excluded in self.EXCLUDED_PATHS):
      continue

  The code checked if full paths like "scripts/lint_skuel_patterns.py" were in individual path parts like ('scripts', 'lint_skuel_patterns.py'), which always returned False.

  ✅ Fix Applied

  Corrected exclusion logic:
  # AFTER (Fixed)
  rel_path = str(py_file.relative_to(self.root_dir))
  if any(excluded in rel_path for excluded in self.EXCLUDED_PATHS):
      continue

  Now checks if exclusion string is contained in the full relative path string.

